{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dangerous Galaxy is a rogue-lite with physics-based combat and extensive ship upgrading, where you explore procedurally generated star systems, manage resources, and fight enemies and boss battles to save the galaxy from evil.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Extensive ship upgrading system:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Different main weapons that you can choose before each run;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Freedom to add or stack upgrades however you want; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Upgrade leveling - Each active upgrade has an upgrade path that you can choose; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Active abilities - The player can hold 4 active abilities at any time.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895800/extras/iamge_1.gif?t=1733382947\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Fun physics-based combat:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every object (including the player) can be pushed away, bumped into or destroyed; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Active abilities (like rockets) can create explosions or gravity-altering effects.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2895800/extras/iamge_2.gif?t=1733382947\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Procedurally generated star systems and levels:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game is split into 5 stages. Each stage has a procedurally generated star system;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Star systems have many levels and each level is procedurally generated (except the boss battles);